title: Karmina 2
description: Following the first Karmina, all the vampires need to take the special potion to be humans. The potion is made by Ghyslain Chatbot and send to Transylvania for the others vampires. Chatbot's wife isn't a vampire yet and she wish to be one. Ghyslain doesn't want to because of all the rules & responsibilities of being a vampire. She throw Ghylsain out of the house without the potion. Ghyslain try to get back in there to get the potion for the others with the help of Vlad. Meanwhile, Philippe comes to Montréal because they're running out of potion in Transylvania. http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0267633/
